PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the COOK'S FERRY BAND surrenders, for an indefinite term, a strip of land running across seven of its reserves in British Columbia (Kumcheen I.R. No. 1, Spences Bridge I.R. No. 4, Lower Shawniken I.R. No. 4A, Pemynoos I.R. No. 9, Pokheitsk I.R. No. 10, Spatsum I.R. No. 11 and Spatsum I.R. No. 11A), for the purpose of granting a right- of-way to the Canadian Pacific Railway Company.
